		<boss_hunt>
			<name>
				<CHS>Lycanthrope Hunt</CHS>
			</name>
			<desc>
				<CHS>Vrikolaks are fierce man-beasts with strong territorial instincts. The rapid industrialization of modern Borgovia led to the deforestation of the Thunderhead Mountains and the shapeshifter tribes lost their hunting grounds. They have also been forced into a constant battle for survival.\nThe Vrikolaks are, understandably, furious. They don’t care that Professor Fulmigati is gone, they are busy unleashing their mindless rage on the population of the metropolis. The Vrikolak attacks reached the level where they’ve left no other choice: they must be hunted down until they learn the lesson.</CHS>
			</desc>
			<objectives>
				<task>
					<CHS>Find and destroy the Vrikolak hordes.</CHS>
				</task>
				<reward>
					<CHS>Kill 1000 Vrikolaks.</CHS>
				</reward>
				<reward2>
					<CHS>Find and kill the Vrikolak leader.</CHS>
				</reward2>
				<kills>
